title: New: Liza Owen – Don't Call Me Baby
body:
Here’s a pop smash for your weekend – Londoner **Liza Owen** calls in some big names on her latest track, _Don’t Call Me Baby_.

Co-written with Ali Tamposi (Bieber’s Let Me Love You), and featuring co-production duties from Jordan Palmer & Robopop (Britney Spears, Charli XCX), this sounds about as current and fresh as possible, perfect for summer playlists.
